title.rendered: First Floor With Patio Terrace For Rent In Chanakyapuri

content.rendered:
This luxury property has 2 bedrooms with attached bathrooms, and the first floor is spread across 1400+ sq ft which has been renovated just recently. it has an open kitchen and a large room with a built-in Bar. marble and granite have been used on the flooring. it has a lovely 750 sqft Patio with a canopy for your outdoor lunch. The property has lots of light and sun and has a serene view of mature trees. the property is close to embassies, American & British Schools, and is located in a very secure neighborhood.
☀️Renovated Recently
☀️Spacious Rooms
☀️Open Kitchen
☀️Patio With Canopy
☀️Marble & Granite Flooring
☀️Secured Neighborhood
☀️Posh Locality
☀️American & British School In Close Proximity
☀️Exclusive Parking
☀️Crystal Clear Title
📞 Call On 9818312077 For Site Visit
Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media
